Data.title: Kidney Bean Curry
Data.description: This delicious vegetarian stew is made in the pressure cooker, using dried kidney beans and a spice paste with garlic, ginger, and onion.

Data.title: Chicken Handi
Data.description: Handi chicken is a delicious dish made with chicken cooked on a low flame for a long time.

Data.title: Dal fry
Data.description: Dal Fry is a delicious and popular Indian lentil recipe that is made with tuvar dal (pigeon pea lentils), onions, tomatoes and spices.
